Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像这样待在坂井同学身边就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔唷 平井组行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 逃吧 吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败我们也没意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦罗嗦罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是锻炼的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能那样的投机 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学 再把身体俯低些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就  就算这么说  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫  莫非是因为我和坂井同学粘在一起才发火的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再追近些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是极限  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学  来了  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二  觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优胜者是捡到便宜的冈田组
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来冈田老师也来啦  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  这也算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是他太太吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 干嘛要追上来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦罗嗦罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且夏娜也总是总是  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年 你也喝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年不能喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真头疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人到底怎么回事啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道大家怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 真抱歉把你丢一边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像把奇怪的东西当枕头了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脖子好疼
